text: "Miracle" is a song by British entertainers Calvin Harris and Ellie Goulding. It was released 10 March 2023. The song entered at number three on the UK Singles Chart and later topped the chart. It also topped the Irish chart. == Track listing == === Beatport exclusive version === === Church version === === Hardwell remix === == References == Category:Calvin Harris songs Category:Ellie Goulding songs Category:2023 songs
